title: tracknest – A SaaS Based Logistic Management System
description: TrackNest is a cloud-based logistics management system that connects drivers, dispatchers, and customers in real time—offering optimized routing, live fleet tracking, instant communication, and transparent delivery updates for faster, smarter, and more reliable operations.

title: Zielo – A Collaboration Platform
description: A web-based platform designed to connect creators and brands for seamless collaborations. Zielo streamlines the partnership process by enabling brands to discover, engage, and work with content creators through a unified dashboard.

title: SocialSense
description: SocialSense is an AI-powered personal branding and LinkedIn content creation platform. Businesses, professionals, and agencies use it to plan, create, and publish engaging content—such as posts, carousels, and content calendars—with efficiency and consistency.
